Package com.nequissimus.university.k1584.ui.elements

Provides UI elements.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractIcon
    Abstract class for icons that will be used by UI labels.
    AbstractLabel
    Abstract class defining essential properties for each label component.
    Arrow
    Arrow connecting two Petri objects.
    Canvas
    This is the main canvas on which all the editing will take place.
    PlaceIcon
    UI Icon for Petri places.
    PlaceLabel
    UI label for place objects.
    Sidebar
    Sidebar UI for adding new elements to the canvas.
    TransitionIcon
    Transition icon that is resizable.
    TransitionLabel
    UI label for transition objects.
    Window
    The main window that holds all the major UI elements, such as the editing canvas, menus etc.
